sun_trine_moon.title: Sun Trine Moon
sun_trine_moon.description: The harmonious trine between Sun and Moon indicates inner integration between conscious will and emotional needs. This creates a balanced, authentic personality.
sun_trine_moon.manifestation: Natural ease in expressing emotions, harmonious relationships, balanced masculine/feminine energies

venus_square_mars.title: Venus Square Mars
venus_square_mars.description: The square between Venus and Mars creates dynamic tension between affection and assertion, receptivity and action. This can manifest as passionate intensity in relationships.
venus_square_mars.manifestation: Passionate attractions, potential for conflict in relationships, learning to balance desire with harmony
